info.name: Dark Wiimmfi Updated
info.description:
This is an updated version of CodyMKW's Dark Wiimmfi style. https://userstyles.org/styles/166076/dark-wiimmfi

This style fixes some of the issues with CodyMKW's style, namely the issue that caused the rankings text on the Competitions page to be unreadable.
info.additionalInfo:
Original style by CodyMKW. https://userstyles.org/styles/166076/dark-wiimmfi

This is release version 1.2.2

Fixed issues:
Fixed duplication of logo in upper-right corner

New changes:
Made tables dark, such as the one on the server status page

Known issues:
At the bottom of the main site in the Wiimmfi Logos section, wiimmfi-light.svg is replaced with wiimmfi-dark.svg. I am not sure if a fix is possible.
